You're excited.

41:14.036 --> 41:22.346
I am excited and I can take, you know, I can just, in a way, I can be completely thrilled and proud and everything because it's their writing.

41:22.366 --> 41:23.968
You know, and I'm happy to be a midwife.

41:25.510 --> 41:27.072
But I'm just

41:27.608 --> 41:34.259
I am so thrilled that other people are... I was right, there is something in this for other people to enjoy.

