41:41.911 --> 41:47.039
I mean, she wasn't a Margaret Sanger or something, you know, who risked her in jail?

41:47.540 --> 41:47.880
No.

41:47.900 --> 41:49.703
And the rest and stuff like that.

41:49.864 --> 41:51.426
No, she wasn't a crusader.

41:51.446 --> 41:52.908
What would the word be for her?

41:53.269 --> 41:54.932
I mean, she sure was dedicated.

41:54.952 --> 41:55.152
Yeah.

